    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "——第8周的早晨。\n经过两个月的治疗，龙姐的身体已经发生了明显的变化。"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "（8周了…龙姐身体的反应一周比一周好。）"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "（她的身体已经完全适应了我的手法。今天能推进到什么程度呢…）"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "",
      "triggerWeeklySettlement": true
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "（客源也很稳定…照这样下去，债务总算能…）"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "",
      "playSE": "door_chime"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "…嗯。",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "龙姐！今天也…等等，您怎么了？脸色看起来不太好…"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "embarrassed",
      "text": "…没什么。只是有点不舒服而已。",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "不舒服？具体是什么感觉呢？"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "shy",
      "text": "…就是，周末的时候…身体一直发热…睡不着。",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "shy",
      "text": "（周末…！那岂不是周六周日都处于欲求不满的状态…）",
      "hideCharacter": true
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "embarrassed",
      "text": "…总觉得，身体深处痒痒的…静不下来。",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "身体深处…是哪个部位呢？"
