      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "angry",
      "text": "…啧。哪个部位…那种事怎么说得出口。",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "shy",
      "text": "（说不出口…那就是那里没错了。太完美了。）",
      "hideCharacter": true
